    <item>
      <title>Meta 积极押注人工智能，推动其股价自 2015 年以来上涨最长时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/meta-s-aggressive-ai-bet-sets-up-stock-s-longest-gain-since-2015</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 的股价有望实现近十年来最长的单日上涨，其最新盈利报告增强了投资者对其人工智能战略的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/meta-s-aggressive-ai-bet-sets-up-stock-s-longest-gain-since-2015</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:46:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达首席执行官黄仁勋将于周五在白宫会见特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nvidia-ceo-huang-to-meet-trump-at-white-house-on-friday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，总统唐纳德·特朗普将于周五在白宫会见英伟达公司首席执行官黄仁勋。几天前，DeepSeek 推出的中国新人工智能模型引发了科技行业领袖的担忧，并导致美国股市暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nvidia-ceo-huang-to-meet-trump-at-white-house-on-friday</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国人工智能部长称使用 DeepSeek 的英国人应警惕风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/brits-using-deepseek-should-be-alert-to-risks-ai-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国人工智能部长费亚尔·克拉克 (Feryal Clark) 表示，使用中国人工智能初创公司 DeepSeek 的聊天机器人的英国人应该警惕其个人数据面临的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/brits-using-deepseek-should-be-alert-to-risks-ai-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:08:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
